name: enemybas.WAD
description: You are sent to infiltrate an enemy base, steal their new rad-suit prototypes, and bust out after defeating the base guards... Barons! Of course, there is always the easy way out, but that would not be very fun... it's for chickens. Can you steal the suits and make it out past the Baron room??? If ya can, you are darn good, but here is another thing... Your commander mentioned something about a stash of over 10 SoulSpheres... where could they be...
